--- title: "Modelos con rasters" author: "Derek Corcoran" date: "08/08, 2023" output: ioslides_presentation: widescreen: true incremental: true --- ## Estudio de abundancia ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} library(rworldxtra) library(raster) library(sf) library(tidyverse) ``` ::: Datos son parte de [PREDICTS](https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1002/ece3.2579) ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} data("countriesHigh") Datos <- read_csv("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/derek-corcoran-barrios/derek-corcoran-barrios.github.io/master/Presentaciones_Espacial/Bombus.csv") ## Miremos los datos Datos <- Datos %>% st_as_sf(coords = c(5, 6), crs = "+proj=longlat +ellps=WGS84 +datum=WGS84 +no_defs +towgs84=0,0,0") Mapa <- countriesHigh %>% st_as_sf() %>% st_crop(Datos) ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} write_sf(Datos, "Datos.shp") ``` ::: ## Vamos graficando ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} ggplot() + geom_sf(data = Mapa) + theme_bw() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Clase8Modelos_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-4-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: ## Agreguemos los puntos ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} ggplot() + geom_sf(data = Mapa) + geom_sf(data = Datos) + theme_bw() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Clase8Modelos_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-5-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: ## Agreguemos colores por especie ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} ggplot() + geom_sf(data = Mapa) + geom_sf(data = Datos, aes(color = species)) + theme_bw() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Clase8Modelos_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-6-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: ## Agreguemos el tamaño por abundancia ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} ggplot() + geom_sf(data = Mapa) + geom_sf(data = Datos, aes(color = species, size = Measurement)) + theme_bw() ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Clase8Modelos_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-7-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: ## o un panel por especie ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} ggplot() + geom_sf(data = Mapa) + geom_sf(data = Datos, aes(size = Measurement)) + theme_bw() + facet_wrap(~species) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Clase8Modelos_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-8-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: ## Resumen - Ver video [tidyverse](https://youtu.be/5tjCeFb2oSk) ::: {.cell} ::: {.cell-output-display} `````{=html}

[Worlclim capas bioclimáticas](https://www.worldclim.org/data/bioclim.html) ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Bioclim <- Bioclim[[c(1, 7, 12, 15)]] plot(Bioclim) ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Clase8Modelos_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-12-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: # Ahora juntemos las bases de datos ## Extracción de datos en los puntos ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Clima <- raster::extract(Bioclim, B_impatiens) %>% as.data.frame() ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ::: {.cell-output-display} `````{=html}

term estimate std.error statistic p.value
(Intercept) 5.9324853 22.8716328 0.2593818 0.7954779
bio1 0.2609852 0.0544680 4.7915291 0.0000024

bio7 -0.0998075 0.1235353 -0.8079272 0.4196262

I(bio15^2) 0.0069000 0.0026550 2.5988754 0.0097086
````` ::: ::: ## Predecir en un raster ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Prediccion <- predict(Bioclim, FitLM) plot(Prediccion, colNA = "black") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Clase8Modelos_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-19-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: - Que porblema hay acá? # GLM ## GLM - Para mas información ver [este video](https://youtu.be/1gLswJR7ZSc) sobre GLMs ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Fit1 <- glm(Measurement ~ bio1 + I(bio1^2) + bio7 + I(bio7^2) + bio12 + I(bio12^2) + bio15 + I(bio15^2), family = poisson, data = B_impatiens) ``` ::: ::: {.cell} ::: {.cell-output-display} `````{=html}

````` ::: ::: ## Predecir en un raster ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Prediccion <- predict(Bioclim, Fit1, type = "response") plot(Prediccion, colNA = "black") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Clase8Modelos_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-22-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: # Dudas? ## Mapa con SF ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} Prediccion_DF <- Prediccion %>% as("SpatialPixelsDataFrame") %>% as.data.frame() %>% rename(Abundancia = layer) ggplot() + geom_tile(data = Prediccion_DF, aes(x = x, y = y, fill = Abundancia)) + geom_sf(data = Mapa, alpha = 0) + theme_bw() + scale_fill_viridis_c() + xlab("") + ylab("") ``` ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Clase8Modelos_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-23-1.png){width=672} ::: ::: ## Mapa con los puntos ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} ggplot() + geom_tile(data = Prediccion_DF, aes(x = x, y = y, fill = Abundancia)) + geom_sf(data = Mapa, alpha = 0) + geom_sf(data = B_impatiens, aes(size = Measurement)) + theme_bw() + scale_fill_viridis_c(option = "plasma") + theme(legend.position = "bottom") + xlab("") + ylab("") ``` ::: ## Mapa con los puntos ::: {.cell} ::: {.cell-output-display} ![](Clase8Modelos_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-25-1.png){width=672} ::: :::
